Cliff-Master		KEY:Trait ~ Cliff-Master		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RegionalTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Cliff-Master],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RegionalTrait]			PRERACE:1,Goblin,RACESUBTYPE=Goblin	PREREGION:1,Varisia	DESC:You are adept at scavenging along the cliffs by the sea, and have become a skilled climber. You gain a +1 trait bonus on all Climb and Survival checks.																							BONUS:SKILL|Climb,Survival|1|TYPE=Trait					SOURCEPAGE:p.16
Goblin Pirate		KEY:Trait ~ Goblin Pirate		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RegionalTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Goblin Pirate],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RegionalTrait]			PRERACE:1,Goblin,RACESUBTYPE=Goblin	PREREGION:1,Shackles	DESC:Although you might prefer life on board a ship, you often end up in the water for some odd reason. You gain a +1 trait bonus on Profession (sailor) and Swim checks, and Swim is always a class skill for you. You might also have a peg leg or a hook for a hand, but that's not so helpful.	BONUS:SKILL|Profession (Sailor),Swim|1|TYPE=Trait	CSKILL:Swim	SOURCEPAGE:p.16
Monkey Goblin		KEY:Trait ~ Monkey Goblin		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RegionalTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Monkey Goblin],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RegionalTrait]			PRERACE:1,Goblin,RACESUBTYPE=Goblin	PREREGION:1,Mediogalti	DESC:You are adept at arboreal activity, and are more at home in the branches of a tree than you are on the ground. You gain a +2 trait bonus on Acrobatics and Climb checks while climbing trees.																												SOURCEPAGE:p.16
Scion of Goblinblood	KEY:Trait ~ Scion of Goblinblood	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RegionalTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Scion of Goblinblood],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RegionalTrait]	PRERACE:1,Goblin,RACESUBTYPE=Goblin	PREREGION:1,Isger		DESC:The fury of the Goblinblood Wars still courses through your veins. Whenever you're within 60 feet of an enemy hobgoblin, you gain a +1 trait bonus on all weapon damage rolls.																															SOURCEPAGE:p.16

