Mother's Teeth			KEY:Trait ~ Mother's Teeth			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.FaithTrait	PREDEITY:1,Lamashtu	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Mother's Teeth],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.FaithTrait]			PRERACE:1,Goblin,RACESUBTYPE=Goblin								DESC:Your teeth are more jagged and pointed than normal. You can make a bite attack for 1d2 points of damage as a secondary attack.																									SOURCEPAGE:p.16
Restless Hunger			KEY:Trait ~ Restless Hunger			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.FaithTrait	PREDEITY:1,Venkelvore	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Restless Hunger],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.FaithTrait]			PRERACE:1,Goblin,RACESUBTYPE=Goblin								DESC:If you have a piece of food (or something a goblin might consider food), you can quickly eat it as part of a charge attack once per day. Doing so increases your speed by 10 feet for 1 round.														SOURCEPAGE:p.16
Strength of the Barghest	KEY:Trait ~ Strength of the Barghest	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.FaithTrait	PREDEITY:1,Hadregash	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Strength of the Barghest],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.FaithTrait]	PRERACE:1,Goblin,RACESUBTYPE=Goblin								DESC:The blood of the barghests is strong in you. Once per day as a free action, you can gain a +2 trait bonus on any Strength check or Strength-based skill check.																			SOURCEPAGE:p.16
Wolf Cub				KEY:Trait ~ Wolf Cub				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.FaithTrait	PREDEITY:1,Zarongel	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Wolf Cub],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.FaithTrait]				PRERACE:1,Goblin,RACESUBTYPE=Goblin								DESC:Your body has clumps of ugly fur, a sure sign of wolf blood! You win! Once per day as a standard action, you can take a deep breath through your nose to gain the scent ability for 1 minute.														SOURCEPAGE:p.16
